## 3. Recommendation Sign-up

3.1. Sign-up UI
   - Display a button or form for users to sign up for daily recommendations.

Implementation:
```javascript
function RecommendationSignup() {
  const [isSignedUp, setIsSignedUp] = useState(false);

  const handleSignup = async () => {
    const response = await fetch('/api/signup-for-recommendations', { method: 'POST' });
    if (response.ok) {
      setIsSignedUp(true);
    }
  };

  return (
    <div>
      {!isSignedUp ? (
        <button onClick={handleSignup}>Sign up for Daily Recommendations</button>
      ) : (
        <p>You're signed up! Click "Find My Song" to get your daily recommendation.</p>
      )}
    </div>
  );
}
```

3.2. Backend Processing
   - When user signs up, update their profile in the database to indicate they want recommendations.

Implementation:
```python
@api_view(['POST'])
def signup_for_recommendations(request):
    user_profile = request.user.profile
    user_profile.wants_recommendations = True
    user_profile.save()
    return Response({'status': 'success'})
```

## 4. Daily Recommendation Process

