## 5. User Feedback and Improvement

5.1. Feedback Collection
   - Provide options for user to give feedback on the recommendation (e.g., thumbs up/down).

Implementation:
```javascript
function Feedback({ trackId }) {
  const submitFeedback = async (isPositive) => {
    await fetch('/api/submit-feedback', {
      method: 'POST',
      body: JSON.stringify({ trackId, isPositive }),
      headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
    });
  };

  return (
    <div>
      <button onClick={() => submitFeedback(true)}>👍</button>
      <button onClick={() => submitFeedback(false)}>👎</button>
    </div>
  );
}
```

5.2. Feedback Processing
   - Store user feedback and use it to adjust future recommendation strategies.

Implementation:
```python
@api_view(['POST'])
